\put(112.8339,-554.0055){\fontsize{9}{1}\usefont{T1}{ptm}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_63426}The transformation of modern electric grids into decentralized smart grids presents new challenges }

\put(58.7008,-586.4055){\fontsize{9}{1}\usefont{T1}{ptm}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_63426}attacks and emergency modes, as well as to develop recommendations on the optimal combination of these methods }
\put(58.7008,-597.2055){\fontsize{9}{1}\usefont{T1}{ptm}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_63426}for ensuring effective cybersecurity under conditions of changin}
\put(318.9808,-597.2055){\fontsize{9}{1}\usefont{T1}{ptm}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_63426}g electrical loads.}
\put(58.7008,-608.0055){\fontsize{9}{1}\usefont{T1}{ptm}{b}{n}\selectfont\color{color_138321}Methods. }
